1. DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the LumaSG plugin source code, documentation, and associated files.
"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software in an environment that:
  * Accepts payments for goods or services
  * Operates a store or marketplace
  * Sells in-game items, ranks, or privileges
  * Monetizes gameplay features or access
  * Generates revenue through advertisements or sponsorships
"Non-Commercial Use" means use limited to environments that:
  * Are completely free-to-play
  * Do not sell any items or services
  * Do not monetize any aspect of gameplay
  * Do not generate any form of revenue
"Compiled Binary" means any executable or distributable form of the Software that is not source code.
"Critical Bug Fix" means any fix that addresses security vulnerabilities, data corruption, server crashes, or other issues that significantly impact the Software's core functionality.
"Derivative Work" means any work based upon the Software or any portion thereof.
"Licensor" means Lumalyte.net.

